links.title: Netflix Stock Falls As Covid-Fueled Growth Slows In Third Quarter
links.description: After experiencing feverish growth during the Covid-19 pandemic, Netflix ( NFLX) subscriber additions slowed to a crawl in the third quarter, giving investors the chills. Netflix stock fell hard Wednesday following the company's disappointing September-quarter earnings report. Late Tuesday, the internet television network reported adding 2.2 million new subscribers worldwide in the third quarter.
